title: Dendy (Nintendo) Soundtracks from 4500 Games +NSF Player +Plugin
description:
Original non-cutted DendyNintendo Soundtracks from almost 4500 most popular games!

Format: NSF & NSFe (nintendo sound files)

This Seeding includes:

1. ~4500 DendyNintendo Original Soundtracks:
  - 2a03.org NSF Collection
  - Akumu's NSF Collection
  - Kevin Horton's NSF collection
  - Slick NSFe collection
  - zophar.net NSF Collection

2. "VirtuaNSF  Virtual NSF" - Special NSF-Player, that can play NSF music
 + VirtuaNSF player can recode NSF to WAV.
 + RUS & ENG languages.

3. in_NotSoFatso.dll - Special Plugin for Winamp or AIMP, that makes able to play NSF in Winamp or Aimp.


External plugin for players installation instruction:
copy in_NotSoFatso.dll plugin to Winamp or Aimp or any other player, that can plug-in external plugins, to it's own Plugins folder, 
for example: "C:Program FilesWinampPlugins"
and then enable plugin in your player's settings.

any questions?
